    hi "Oh, quel caffè."

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2229
translate it a1_saturday_shanghaied_69a0892f:

    # mi "Tea shop! It's called the Shanghai. China is the birthplace of tea, you know. Come on, Hicchan! I'll even treat you today!"
    mi "Sala da tè! Si chiama Shanghai. La Cina è il luogo di nascita del tè, sai. Forza, Hicchan! Offrirò persino io, oggi!"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2234
translate it a1_saturday_shanghaied_c364b8f3:

    # mi "Ah… not me, not me, I mean Shicchan! Ahaha~!"
    mi "Ah… non io, non io, voglio dire Shicchan! Ahaha~!"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2236
translate it a1_saturday_shanghaied_73bbbe7f:

    # hi "I don't know…"
    hi "Non so…"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2241
translate it a1_saturday_shanghaied_187570af:

    # mi "It's nice, it's really relaxing! It's like… half café, half restaurant, half sophisticated, half… library…"
    mi "È carino, è veramente rilassante! È come… metà caffè, metà ristorante, metà sofisticato, metà… biblioteca…"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2243
translate it a1_saturday_shanghaied_67aaa788:

    # "What?"
    "Cosa?"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2245
translate it a1_saturday_shanghaied_37388ddb:

    # hi "That's a lot of halves."
    hi "Quelle sono un sacco di metà."

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2247
translate it a1_saturday_shanghaied_c5c83e3e:

    # "But Misha doesn't seem to notice that."
    "Ma Misha non sembra accorgersi del mio commento."

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2252
translate it a1_saturday_shanghaied_2241ccbc:

    # mi "So~! Come on, it's not often that we have this much free time!"
    mi "Così~! Dai, non capita spesso che abbiamo così tanto tempo libero!"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2257
