    mi "Perché?"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:3380
translate it a1_saturday_shanghaied_5839b852:

    # hi "Shizune. I didn't know that she liked to joke around like that."
    hi "Shizune. Non sapevo le piacesse scherzare in quel modo."

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:3382
translate it a1_saturday_shanghaied_ff7d4db8:

    # "What I mean to say is, I didn't know that she could act so girlish. It was actually pretty cute."
    "Quel che voglio dire è, non sapevo che potesse comportarsi in modo così femminile. A dire il vero era piuttosto grazioso."

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:3387
translate it a1_saturday_shanghaied_79e1c8a4:

    # mi "You would be surprised, Hicchan."
    mi "Resteresti sorpreso, Hicchan."

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:3389
translate it a1_saturday_shanghaied_5d2e01f8:

    # hi "Well, I didn't know you and her were so close, either, the first time I saw you."
    hi "Beh, non sapevo neanche che tu e lei foste così inseparabili, la prima volta che vi ho viste."

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:3391
translate it a1_saturday_shanghaied_bfa2ec07:

    # "I've always been curious as to how these two met."
